durbin.util
Class Table

java.lang.Object
  groovy.lang.GroovyObjectSupport
      durbin.util.Table

class Table
extends GroovyObjectSupport

***************************************************************** A 2D table of objects with methods to read from file, iterate over rows or columns, and support for Groovy closures. A Table is a 2D collection of cells. Table cells can be accessed by index or by name. ******************************************************************
